      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPREMEDREAM (1) lines up for the first time. By Art Major and hails from the K L Howlett stable. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Showed some ability when a minor placegetter in a recent trial and makes plenty of appeal. LETS RATTLNROLL (9) was 17 metres away in second at this track over 1730m last start at his first run back from a spell. Has to contend with a very wide draw but rates a primary contender in this comparable race. ROCKNROLL DILINGER (6) is better than her last-start ninth over 1730m at this circuit. Can bounce back. LADY OF LEITH (3) disappointed last time but is a chance based on a good third over 1684m at Pinjarra two runs back. Worth another chance.",
